title: Demo Status
new-page: true
is-special: true

= Civic Reform Dashboard

This status scene is the sidebar/dashboard. It displays Q variables that cards,
advisors, and events change. In Studio, the Variables view explains where each
variable is read or written.

Calendar: [+ demo_year +] / [+ demo_month +]

Latest civic wire: [+ news_1 +]

[+ news_1_desc +]

[? if news_2 != "" : Previous wire: [+ news_2 +] ?]
[? if news_3 != "" : Earlier wire: [+ news_3 +] ?]

Resources: [+ demo_resources +]

Volunteer support: [+ demo_support : qdemo_level +]

Advisor trust: [+ demo_advisor_trust : qdemo_level +]

Card progress: [+ demo_card_progress : qdemo_level +]

Chain pressure: [+ demo_pressure : qdemo_level +]

Public attention: [+ demo_public_attention : qdemo_level +]

Case strength: [+ demo_case_strength : qdemo_level +]

Cabinet balance: [+ demo_cabinet_balance : qdemo_level +]

Reform mandate: [+ demo_reform_mandate : qdemo_level +]

Opposition heat: [+ demo_opposition_heat : qdemo_level +]

Press risk: [+ demo_press_risk : qdemo_level +]

Legislative path: [+ demo_legislative_path : qdemo_level +]

[? if demo_support > 0 : Volunteer support is active because a briefing, card, or advisor raised it. ?]
[? if demo_conflict > 0 : The office has recorded conflict from an earlier choice. ?]
[? if demo_card_progress > 0 : The action deck has changed project state. ?]
[? if demo_advisor_trust > 0 : The advisor lane has contributed trust. ?]
[? if demo_chain_seen > 0 : The civic reform chain has started. ?]
[? if demo_resolution_seen > 0 : The civic reform chain has reached a conclusion. ?]
[? if demo_budget_leak_seen > 0 : Budget leak popup has appeared in the monthly docket. ?]
[? if demo_polling_shock_seen > 0 : Polling shock popup has appeared in the monthly docket. ?]
[? if demo_council_deadlock_seen > 0 : Council deadlock popup has appeared in the monthly docket. ?]
[? if demo_resolution_result >= 3 : Final result: clean public mandate. ?]
[? if demo_resolution_result = 2 : Final result: contested reform survives. ?]
[? if demo_resolution_result = 1 : Final result: cabinet compromise keeps the work alive. ?]
[? if demo_resolution_result < 0 : Final result: reform drifts without enough support. ?]

@organization

= Organization

Use this section for capacity, volunteers, funding, membership, or other core
organization variables.

@cards

= Cards

Use this section for hand, deck, cooldown, and card-progress variables.

@advisors

= Advisors

Use this section for advisor-like or Circle-style persistent cards.

@politics

= Public Mood

Use this section for public support, opposition pressure, election context, or
other map/dashboard variables.

@complex_chain

= Complex Event Chain

Use this section for pressure, case strength, cabinet balance, reform mandate,
opposition heat, and other variables read by the civic reform chain.
